Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: First Rockdale IV is located in the Class A master-planned Rockdale Distribution Park in Wilson County, Tennessee. The site is strategically located between I-40 and I-24 on the 840 Loop, with immediate access via Couchville Pike and Maddox Road, and a half hour from Nashville International Airport. First Rockdale IV includes a 500,240 square-foot cross dock distribution center featuring 40’ clear heights, 185’ truck courts, an ESFR sprinkler system, 220 car parking spaces, and 142 trailer parking spaces.
